<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a55ac91-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s6307"><num value="6307">§ 6307.</num><heading> Reporting</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Not later than 48 business hours after the conclusion of a professional boxing match, the supervising boxing commission shall report the results of such boxing match and any related suspensions to each boxer registry.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7a55ac92-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/272/s8">Pub. L. 104–272, § 8</ref>, <date date="1996-10-09">Oct. 9, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3311">110 Stat. 3311</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id7a55ac93-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id7a55ac94-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id7a55ac95-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1997-07-01">July 1, 1997</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/272/s23/2">section 23(2) of Pub. L. 104–272</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s6301">section 6301 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
